35.htm |archive-date=March 8, 2005 |publisher=United States Department of State  |location=Washington, D.C. |access-date=February 19, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Embry-Riddle (2019)\">{{cite web |title=ERAU Alumni Class Notes |url=https://alumni.erau.edu/s/867/social.aspx?sid=867&gid=1&pgid=3410 |date=December 2019 |publisher=Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University |location=Daytona Beach, Florida |access-date=March 20, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"F-4 Society (2001)\">{{cite book |author= |title=F-4 Phantom II Society |edition=Illustrated |publisher=Turner Publishing Company |year=2001 |isbn=978-1563116384 |p=91 |quote=at this time (mid-1970s), most (USAF ROTC) pilot candidates were not getting Undergraduate Pilot Training slots |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=zG5MBLx6mJgC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q=USAF%20ROTC%20not%20getting%20UPT%20slots&f=false |access-date=March 20, 2020 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fact Sheet 5RS (2019)\">{{cite web |url= http://www.afhra.af.mil/About-Us/Fact-Sheets/Display/Article/432067/5-reconnaissance-squadron-acc/ |title=5 Reconnaissance Squadron (ACC) |date=July 31, 2019 |website=Air Force Historical Research Agency |publisher=United States Air Force |access-date=February 7, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fauquier Now (2019)\">{{cite web |last= |first= |title=U-2 pilot elected chairman of Cold War Museum board |url=https://www.fauquiernow.com/fauquier_news/entry/fauquier-u-2-pilot-elected-chairman-of-cold-war-museum-2019 |website=fauquiernow.com |date=December 4, 2019 |access-date=February 5, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Free Dictionary Provisional\">{{cite web |title=Provisonal unit\" |url=https://www.thefreedictionary.com/provisional+unit |date= |website=thefreedictionary.com |publisher=Farlex, Inc |access-date=February 10, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Freedom Museum (2016)\">{{cite news |author= |title= Colonel Charles \u2018Chuck\u2019 Wilson to Speak at the Freedom Museum |url= https://potomaclocal.com/events/colonel-charles-chuck-wilson-speak-freedom-museum/ |work=Potomac Local  |publisher=Potomac Local Media LLC |date=June 14, 2016 |access-date=March 10, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Graham (1996)\">{{cite book |last1=Graham |first1=Richard |title=SR-71 Revealed: The Untold Story |date=1996 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/sr71revealedinsi00colr/page/38 38\u201339] |isbn=0760301220 |url=https://archive.org/details/sr71revealedinsi00colr/page/38 |publisher=Zenith Press |edition=First}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"HB63 Passes (2016)\">{{cite web |last= |first= |url= https://vfw7916.org/di/vfw/v2/default.asp?pid=63136&d=y&subid=31286 |title= HB 63 Passes Virginia General Assembly |work = The Virginia Veteran |publisher= |date=April 2016 |p=3 |access-date=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ISO Director (2002)\">{{cite web |title=ISO Director Col. Charles Wilson |url=https://2001-2009.state.gov/t/pm/iso/15947.htm |date=September 2002 |publisher=United States Department of State  |location=Washington, D.C. |access-date=March 3, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ISO Functions (2002)\">{{cite web |title=Department of State Visits by Senior Military Officers |url= https://2001-2009.state.gov/t/pm/iso/15973.htm |date=September 2002 |publisher=United States Department of State  |location=Washington, D.C. |access-date=March 3, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Jenkins (2012)\">{{cite book |last=Jenkins |first=Dennis R. |title= Dressing for Altitude: U.S. Aviation Pressure Suits\u2014Wiley Post to Space Shuttle |publisher=National Aeronautics and Space Administration |year=2012 |isbn=978-0-16-090110-2 |location= |url= https://www.nasa.gov/pdf/683215main_DressingAltitude-ebook.pdf |access-date=February 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Norris (2010)\">{{cite book |last=Norris |first=Pat |title=Watching Earth from Space: How Surveillance Helps Us -- and Harms Us |publisher=Springer Science & Business Media |year=2010 |isbn=978-1-4419-6938-5 |location= |url= |access-date=}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\